
ILSVRC2012 Datasets Download Description

Users can either subscribe with an edu email address to apply to download 
the ILSVRC2012 dataset from ImageNet or use any top-3 torrent client application 
to download the dataset. It has the size of 160+ GiB and takes about 3~7 days to 
download depending on your regions and network providers. 

1. ImageNet 

With regard to the official ImageNet, users can directly download from ImageNet 
with the following download link. 

http://image-net.org/download-images

Goolge provides a non-stop tools to download the dataset, please follow up the 
Google description witjh the following link. 

https://www.tensorflow.org/datasets/catalog/imagenet2012


2.Other channels

Users can download the dataset from anyone of the top-3 torrents from the academic 
torrents.com. 


https://academictorrents.com/browse.php?search=ILSVRC2012
